Question:
Consider following database Cricket_play(p_id, Name, Address) Matches(Match_code,
match_date, match_place) Score(p_id, match_code, score) Write following queries in SQL
i) List player name, match_date, match_place, and score of each player
4
ii) List all those players, whose maximum score is higher than 50 

Practical:

Microsoft Windows [Version 10.0.22631.5624]
